Determine whether this social media post from Donald Trump is an insult to Kamala Harris. Simply return "yes" or "no".
content: Under Kamala, we are now in a manufacturing recession, with manufacturing contracting in 22 out of the last 23 months. We have lost nearly 50,000 manufacturing jobs this year alone, car sales are down 38% since I left, the share of domestically produced cars sold has dropped significantly—and the U.S. trade deficit in automobiles has exploded by over $50 billion to an all-time high…
